imdb.title: Super Dragon Ball Heroes
imdb.plot: The Z-Fighters set out to rescue Trunks from a prison planet.

episodes.title: Goku basasu Goku! Kangoku Wakusei de Chozetsu Batoru Kaimaku!
episodes.plot: Goku, Vegeta and Mai travel to the mysterious Prison Planet in an attempt to rescue Future Trunks, who has been captured by an unknown force.

episodes.title: Boso shita Goku! Aku no saiya-jin o abare!
episodes.plot: An evil Saiyan called Cunber escapes his prison cell and attacks Goku, Vegeta and Mai.

episodes.title: Saikyoo no kagayaki! Bejittoburu kaioken sakuretsu!
episodes.plot: Vegito fights Kanba.

episodes.title: Gekiko! Supa Fyu tojo!
episodes.plot: Goku, Vegeta, Future Trunks and Golden Cooler initiate a game plan to defeat the powerful Cunber.

episodes.title: Saikyo no senshi! Supa Saiya-jin fo Bejitto!!
episodes.plot: Xeno Goku and Xeno Vegeta challenge Cunber to a battle.

episodes.title: I'll Finish This!! Ultra Instinct goes into Operation!
episodes.plot: After the Prison Planet's barrier is destroyed, an enraged Fu battles Xeno Goku and Xeno Vegeta.

episodes.title: The Curtain Rises on the Universal Conflict Arc!
episodes.plot: A battle erupts on Universe 6, and Cabba, Kale, Caulifla and Hit are defending it.

episodes.title: The Ultimate Worst Warriors Invade! Universe 6 Demolished!
episodes.plot: In the battle to survive and defeat Oren and Kamin, they transform their bodies into energy and possess Kale and Caulifla, to attack Cabba and Hit but Vegeta, Trunks and Hit develop a plan to defeat them.

episodes.title: Goku Revived!! Strongest Vs. Strongest Collide!
episodes.plot: A battle erupts between Jiren and Cunber after Hearts and his gang deploy an attack upon Universe 11.

episodes.title: Counterattack! Fierce Attack! Goku and Vegeta!
episodes.plot: After saving Vegeta from Oren, Goku powers up to confront Hearts and his gang.

episodes.title: Fierce Fight! Universe 11's Decisive Battle!
episodes.plot: The battle continues between Goku and Heart's gang. Meanwhile, Fu observes the fight from his new laboratory and prepares to unleash his new robotic fighter.

episodes.title: Super Warriors Gather! Universe 7's Decisive Battle!
episodes.plot: Goku and Vegeta's fight is taken to Universe 7, after Hearts and his gang plan to destroy it.

episodes.title: Supa Hatsu sansen! Daichi yurugasu zenkai batoru!
episodes.plot: Goku powers up to Super Saiyan Blue in hopes of defeating Hearts.

episodes.title: The Menacing Universe Seed! Kamioren's Rampage!!
episodes.plot: After powering up, Hearts uses his crystals to enhance his strength and defeats Goku with a single blow. Meanwhile, Piccolo and 17 are able to injure Kamioren again; Kamioren appears to be off-balance, so Hearts decides to assist them. He shrinks the Universe Seed to a small size using his crystals and implants it into Kamioren, causing them to undergo a monstrous transformation that increases their power even further. In this state, Kamioren easily defeats Piccolo and 17, so Vegeta and Trunks go to assist them. All four fighters attack Kamioren together, but are ...

episodes.title: Send Kamioren Flying! Overwhelming! Ultra Instinct!
episodes.plot: Goku begins fighting Kamioren, and the two seem to be fairly evenly matched in terms of power, until Goku reaches the mastered level of Ultra Instinct and easily deflects Kamioren's attacks. He overwhelms Kamioren with help from the others, damaging them with a Kamehameha and a barrage of energy blasts before shattering their core with a final punch, causing their body to disintegrate. Goku loses his Ultra Instinct again, while Hearts expresses sorrow over the deaths of Kamin and Oren, before retrieving the now fully-charged Universe Seed from Kamioren's remains. ...

episodes.title: Zamasu vs Universe 7! Ambition's End!
episodes.plot: Vegeta and the others try to attack Hearts while he is absorbing the Universe Seed, but Zamasu intervenes and deflects their attacks. Trunks questions why Zamasu would work with a mortal like Hearts, but Zamasu explains that he is only working with Hearts in order to defeat the Omni-King, after which he still intends to destroy all mortals. Zamasu quickly incapacitates Vegeta, Trunks, Piccolo and 17, leaving Goku as the only one left standing. Goku is losing too, but Jiren and Hit arrive to rescue him and join the fight, having been sent by the Kaioshins of their ...

episodes.title: The Ultimate Godslayer! Hearts is Born!
episodes.plot: Hearts launches a simultaneous attack on the Z-Fighters, who struggle to fight back. Goku powers up to Super Saiyan Blue and attacks him, but Hearts easily knocks him away and then uses a massive gravity attack to take down all of the fighters at once. As the others recover, Jiren and Hit go after Hearts again, while Goku suggests that he and Vegeta use the Fusion Dance to make themselves strong enough to take on Hearts' new power.
